OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,FThe Deputy First Minister Huw Irranca-
OL,7,FDavies MS, who has responsibility for
OL,8,FClimate Change and Rural Affairs, has
OL,9,Foutlined the new Sustainable Farming
OL,10,FScheme today.
OL,12,FWhat is the Scheme?
OL,14,FThe Sustainable Farming Scheme is said
OL,15,Fto be The Welsh Government's way to
OL,16,Fsupport farmers, land management and
OL,17,Fsustainable food production from 2026
OL,18,Fonwards.
