OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,FIt will pay farmers for actions
OL,7,Fresulting in environmental, animal
OL,8,Fwelfare and social outcomes above the
OL,9,Flegal requirements.
OL,11,FTo be eligible, farmers will be
OL,12,Frequired to manage at least 10% of
OL,13,Ftheir farm as habitat.
OL,15,FFarmers will be required to carry out
OL,16,F'universal actions' for which they
OL,17,Fwould receive the 'universal baseline
OL,18,Fpayment'.
OL,20,F'Optional' and 'collaborative' actions
OL,21,Fcan be done for additional payments.
