OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,FFarmers can chose to join the scheme
OL,7,Fbut must undertake all 'universal
OL,8,Factions' and have sole control of the
OL,9,Fland to receive the money.
OL,11,FThere are 12 'universal actions',
OL,12,Fwhich include soil health, habitat
OL,13,Fmaintenance and tree and hedgerow
OL,14,Fplanting opportunities.
OL,16,FWhy is it controversial?
OL,18,FLast year thousands of farmers
OL,19,Fprotested outside the Senedd as a
OL,20,Fresult of the proposed Sustainable
OL,21,FFarming Scheme.
