OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,FThe backlash is based on the fact
OL,7,Ffarmers will have to meet strict
OL,8,Fenvironmental targets in return for
OL,9,Fgovernment funding.
OL,11,FThere are fears it won't work for all
OL,12,Ffarmers due to complications around
OL,13,Fland ownership and rights to land.
OL,15,FThe National Farmers Union in Wales
OL,16,Fsays that the scheme must work for
OL,17,Fevery farm in Wales. Aled Jones,
OL,18,FPresident of NFU Cymru, says that
OL,19,Fagriculture is the bedrock for Wales'
OL,20,Ffood and drinks sector.
