OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,F"NFU Cymru has long been clear that
OL,7,Fthe Sustainable Farming Scheme must
OL,8,Fprovide at least the same level of
OL,9,Fstability to farm businesses, rural
OL,10,Fcommunities and the supply chain as
OL,11,Fthe Basic Payment Scheme does
OL,12,Fcurrently.
OL,14,F"In March 2024, NFU Cymru placed 5,500
OL,15,Fpairs of wellies on the steps of the
OL,16,FSenedd, a deeply moving and poignant
OL,17,Fdepiction of the potential job losses
OL,18,Fon farm forecast by an impact
OL,19,Fassessment of a previous version of
OL,20,Fthe Sustainable Farming Scheme.
