OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,F"It is imperative that the revised
OL,7,Fscheme and budget attached to the SFS,
OL,8,Fwhich is expected to be published this
OL,9,Fweek, avoids such a shocking impact on
OL,10,Fone of Wales' iconic sectors.
OL,12,FThe SFS must work for all farming
OL,13,Fsectors and areas of Wales and help
OL,14,Fensure that Welsh farming can continue
OL,15,Fto underpin the #9.3 billion food and
OL,16,Ffarming supply chain."
OL,18,FWhen will the Scheme come into play?
