OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,FFrom 2026 you will have the choice to
OL,7,Fenter the Sustainable Farming Scheme
OL,8,For remain with the Basic Payment
OL,9,FScheme which will be phased out by
OL,10,F2029.
OL,12,FThe current scheme that farmers
OL,13,Freceive funding from will be worth
OL,14,Fjust 60% of its current value. That
OL,15,Fmeans that if farmers want to receive
OL,16,Fmore money from the Welsh Government,
OL,17,Fthey will have to sign up to the
OL,18,FSustainable Farming Scheme next year.
OL,20,FWhat the Welsh Government hope it will
OL,21,Fachieve?
