OL,3,CWhat does the new subsidy mean for
OL,4,CWelsh farmers?
OL,6,F"Our ambition is to see a thriving and
OL,7,Fconfident agriculture sector in Wales,
OL,8,Fthat is built around innovation and
OL,9,Fgrowth."
OL,11,F"Supports farmers in Wales to produce
OL,12,Fworld class, high-quality, food whilst
OL,13,Fcaring for the environment, tackling
OL,14,Fand adapting to climate change and
OL,15,Fbuilding resilience for those who will
OL,16,Fwork and care for this precious land
OL,17,Fin the years to come."
